(Using the less-than comparison operator on strings)

Str is "foo"
TrueStr is "OK"
FalseStr is "LieS"
EmptyStr is ""

Say "strings aren't less than booleans"
Rightness is right
Wrongness is wrong
say TrueStr is less than Rightness
say TrueStr is less than Wrongness
say EmptyStr is less than Rightness
say false is less than FalseStr
say false is less than TrueStr
say false is less than "true"
say false is less than "false"
say false is less than ""

